  "title": "Sous Chef",
  "description": "<p>Benefits: AL, Medical Leave, Incentive</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Requirement:</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>At least three years relevant experience in a similar capacity</p>\n<p>Basic kitchen operations knowledge</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Job Description</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Follow the instructions of head chef.</li>\n  <li>Ordering of raw materials.</li>\n  <li>Budget and inventory control.</li>\n  <li>New menu creation.</li>\n  <li>Lead the team when the head chef is not present.</li>\n  <li>Maintain kitchen hygiene and safety before, during and after operations.</li>\n  <li>Daily food preparation and restocking.</li>\n  <li>Cooking food up to standard, following the recipes given.</li>\n</ul>",
